{"tid":1179290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《自我歷險叢書》出版社控告 Netflix《黑鏡：潘達斯奈基》侵權","createTime":"2019-05-31T04:15:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T12:37:16.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"3c7777cedd1197430d876f089e8548a97f5319f9","tid":1179290,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:15:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-ZdXUAHlP8Zg/VZe3i2VDKUI/AAAAAAAABMg/R9ucaFEGBDA/s400/CYOA%2BBook2.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZdXUAHlP8Zg%2FVZe3i2VDKUI%2FAAAAAAAABMg%2FR9ucaFEGBDA%2Fs400%2FCYOA%252BBook2.JPG&h=ad3a9c06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNetflix 之前上映的《黑鏡：潘達斯奈基》互動劇集扭轉了傳統劇集的模式，讓觀衆自行選擇劇情發展，可導致不同結局發生。這樣的模式讓人聯想起以前的多路線小說《自我歷險叢書》。不期然這個系列的出版社最近就向法院提告。<br />\n<br />\n《自我歷險叢書（Choose Your Own Adventure）》是一系列經典的多路線兒童小說，讀者可以在故事的不同進度作出不同選擇，揭到不同頁來顯示選擇劇情發展，最後到達不同的結局。其出版社 Chooseco LLC 表示，Netflix 侵犯了他們的商標，而 Netflix 之前其實有嘗試向 Chooseco LLC 洽談商標授權事宜但最後談判告吹，最後 Netflix 就自行推出《黑鏡：潘達斯奈基》。<br />\n<br />\nChooseco LLC 表示，《黑鏡：潘達斯奈基》其中一個情節甚至有提及《自我歷險叢書》，其劇集的黑暗和暴力內容，更對於這一兒童書籍系列帶來負面影響。Chooseco LLC 方面向 Netflix 索償 2,500 萬美元，Netflix 則仍然未回應事件。其實互動式劇集並非今次由 Netflix 首創，而 Netflix 自己也有推出過類似的互動式劇集，不過 Chooseco LLC 表示之前對於 Netflix 的另一個互動劇集已經發出了停止並終止要求，意味之後可能會有進一步法律行動。"},{"pid":"d83fc27b72aad075cc59fb39a67482dba895df69","tid":1179290,"uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:16:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/cl-books-set3-1200x660.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2Fcl-books-set3-1200x660.jpg&h=415e1c83&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c268a6e80b3a2433d7fb7a6d15edb662dfdbac29","tid":1179290,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:16:24.000Z","msg":"貪錢就貪錢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d85cbb394091a39df8b9c579158a991ef18f631b","tid":1179290,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:16:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/01/13/bandersnatch-lawsuit-choose-your-own-adventure-netflix/movie-2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F01%2F13%2Fbandersnatch-lawsuit-choose-your-own-adventure-netflix%2Fmovie-2%2F&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoH4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=1a0add4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/01/13/bandersnatch-lawsuit-choose-your-own-adventure-netflix/movie-2/</a>"},{"pid":"c5aca2940c00b9b8ac64424f4e943d71471d91ec","tid":1179290,"uid":88374,"like":3,"dislike":48,"score":-45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:17:58.000Z","msg":"netflix真係狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37b42949dbcee32cf78a885c599cf3cb84308e08","tid":1179290,"uid":78971,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:20:40.000Z","msg":"其出版社 Chooseco LLC 表示，Netflix 侵犯了他們的商標，而 Netflix 之前其實有嘗試向 Chooseco LLC 洽談商標授權事宜但最後談判告吹，最後 Netflix 就自行推出《黑鏡：潘達斯奈基》。<br />\n<br />\n恃住自己大公司就唔撚理版權？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"037f6d25bb67995260841a9f1fb572a532a33eb0","tid":1179290,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:27:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/061019_d8a42bee6d7226331b2ea10158a6e573.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F061019_d8a42bee6d7226331b2ea10158a6e573.png&h=6e1c5953&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba751ee4547df33170a20513e819f493728de3b1","tid":1179290,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d83fc27b72aad075cc59fb39a67482dba895df69","tid":1179290,"uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score